llScreen":true}]}],["$","p",null,{"children":["What if a bot could play Pokémon from start to finish — with zero human intervention? That's exactly the challenge behind two experimental projects: ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"FireredBOT"}]," and ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"PokeAI"}],". Together, they push the boundaries of automation, contextual intelligence, and computational vision applied to classic games."]}],["$","hr",null,{"className":"border-t-2 border-foreground/20 my-6"}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-primary border-b-2 border-primary pb-1","children":"FireredBOT — The Bot That Plays Pokémon FireRed on Its Own"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"flex items-center space-x-2 text-primary overflow-hidden text-ellipsis whitespace-nowrap","children":["🔗 ",["$","a",null,{"href":"https://github.com/allanzinhodev/fireredBOT","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer","className":"hover:underline","children":"github.com/allanzinhodev/fireredBOT"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"children":"FireredBOT is a Python-based automation system capable of playing Pokémon FireRed fully autonomously. No direct commands, no human input — the bot makes every decision on its own."}],["$","h4",null,{"className":"text-lg font-bold mt-6 mb-2","children":"What it does"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Explores maps automatically using a custom pathfinding system that identifies walkable paths, entrances, exits, and territory boundaries"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Battles strategically, prioritizing moves based on type effectiveness, base damage, and remaining PP"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Automatically catches Pokémon, expanding the Pokédex without any human help"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Manages the inventory and returns to the Pokémon Center whenever needed"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Reads emulator memory (VBA-RR or mGBA) in real time, tracking HP, player position, wild Pokémon IDs, and game state"}]]}],["$","h4",null,{"className":"text-lg font-bold mt-6 mb-2","children":"Twitch Integration"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"One of the most creative features is the Twitch API integration: viewers can send commands in the chat and influence the bot's behavior in real time — switching between exploration, catching, battling modes, or even daring the bot to take risks. It's automation with a layer of live interactivity."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"bg-primary/10 p-4 border-l-4 border-primary italic","children":"✅ Goal achieved: the bot works as intended, handles complex tasks, and makes context-aware decisions. The project is complete and will not receive further updates."}],["$","hr",null,{"className":"border-t-2 border-foreground/20 my-6"}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-primary border-b-2 border-primary pb-1","children":"PokeAI — Pokémon Crystal Automation in Pure Lua"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"flex items-center space-x-2 text-primary overflow-hidden text-ellipsis whitespace-nowrap","children":["🔗 ",["$","a",null,{"href":"https://github.com/allanzinhodev/pokeAI","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer","className":"hover:underline","children":"github.com/allanzinhodev/pokeAI"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"children":"PokeAI grew out of the same experiments but took a completely different direction — focused on Pokémon Crystal and rebuilt from scratch in pure Lua, running directly inside the VBA-RR emulator with no Python dependencies."}],["$","h4",null,{"className":"text-lg font-bold mt-6 mb-2","children":"A \"computational vision\" through memory"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Instead of capturing screenshots or using vision models, PokeAI reads tile offsets directly from the game's RAM, building a real-time representation of the world. This allows the bot to identify:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Collisions, walls, and obstacles"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Doors and building entrances"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"NPCs and available interactions"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"The current battle menu state (Fight, Pokémon, Pack, Run)"}]]}],["$","h4",null,{"className":"text-lg font-bold mt-6 mb-2","children":"System features"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Adaptive navigation with natural obstacle avoidance"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Automatic Pokémon catching system"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Automatic Pokémon and move switching in battle"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Anti-freeze systems to keep the bot running smoothly"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Battle intelligence script for wild encounters and trainer fights"}],["$","li",null,{"children":["Modular Lua architecture: ",["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-foreground/10 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-mono","children":"main.lua"}],", ",["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-foreground/10 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-mono","children":"battle.lua"}],", ",["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-foreground/10 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-mono","children":"move.lua"}],", ",["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-foreground/10 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-mono","children":"map.lua"}]]}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"bg-green-500/10 p-4 border-l-4 border-green-500 italic mt-4","children":["The project is in active experimental phase, and future improvements may include OCR, neural networks, or Python reintegration for more complex analysis. You can follow the development live on ",["$","a",null,{"href":"https://twitch.tv/allaorodrigues","className":"text-primary hover:underline","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer","children":"twitch.tv/allaorodrigues"}],"."]}],["$","hr",null,{"className":"border-t-2 border-foreground/20 my-6"}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-primary border-b-2 border-primary pb-1","children":"Why These Projects Matter"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Beyond being fascinating projects in their own right, FireredBOT and PokeAI showcase concepts with real-world applications: memory reading and manipulation, contextual decision systems, pathfinding, complex task automation, and live platform integration. They are educational experiments that show how software engineering can turn a nostalgic game into an AI laboratory."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 p-4 border-2 border-foreground text-center bg-foreground/5 text-sm sm:text-base","children":[["$","p",null,{"children":["Developed by Allan Rodrigues — ",["$","a",null,{"href":"https://linkedin.com/in/allanzinho","className":"text-primary hover:underline break-all","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer","children":"linkedin.com/in/allanzinho"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"children":["Watch it live at ",["$","a",null,{"href":"https://twitch.tv/allaorodrigues","className":"text-primary hover:underline break-all","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer","children":"twitch.tv/allaorodrigues"}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"w-full flex justify-center my-8","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center space-x-2","children":[[["$","div","0",{"className":"w-2 h-2 bg-black","style":{"boxShadow":"2px 2px 0 0 #ff1493"}}],["$","div","1",{"className":"w-2 h-2 bg-black","style":{"boxShadow":"2px 2px 0 0 #ff1493"}}],["$","div","2",{"className":"w-2 h-2 bg-black","style":{"boxShadow":"2px 2px 0 0 #ff1493"}}]],["$","div",null,{"className":"w-32 h-4 bg-black","style":{"boxShadow":"4px 4px 0 0 #ff1493"}}],[["$","div","0",{"className":"w-2 h-2 bg-black","style":{"boxShadow":"2px 2px 0 0 #ff1493"}}],["$","div","1",{"className":"w-2 h-2 bg-black","style":{"boxShadow":"2px 2px 0 0 #ff1493"}}],["$","div","2",{"className":"w-2 h-2 bg-black","style":{"boxShadow":"2px 2px 0 0 #ff1493"}}]]]}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 text-center","children":["$","a",null,{"href":"https://pokeai.example.com","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer","className":"inline-flex ite